Sentencas: Single phase polycrystalline BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.1Yb0.1O3 - delta electrolyte material was prepared by solid state reaction route.
Titulo: Robust doped BaCeO3-δ electrolyte for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Rietveld analysis of the XRD data confirms the tetragonal symmetry in the I4/mcm space group with unit cell parameters of a = b = 6.0567(3) and c = 8.5831(5) .
Titulo: Robust doped BaCeO3-δ electrolyte for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The addition of ZnO as a sintering additive was found to reduce the sintering temperature and enhance both overall sinterability and grain growth.
Titulo: Robust doped BaCeO3-δ electrolyte for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Sintering temperature was reduced by 200-300 A degrees C, and a very high relative density of about 98% was achieved at 1400 A degrees C. Impedance spectroscopy in humidified 5% H-2/Ar atmosphere shows that the protonic conductivity at 600 A degrees C was 8.60 x 10(-3) S cm(-1).
Titulo: Robust doped BaCeO3-δ electrolyte for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Thermal analysis performed in pure CO2 atmosphere shows very good chemical stability up to 1200 A degrees C. Good biaxial flexure strength of 100-200 MPa was reported which makes this material a promising electrolyte material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Robust doped BaCeO3-δ electrolyte for IT-SOFCs
